Components of Hadoop 1.x :

HDFS-
1.Name Node-Stores MetaData about Data Nodes(no. of blocks , slave node details,locations)
2.Data Node-Places in SlaveNodes. Stores application data.

MapReduce-
1.Job Tracker- Assigns MapReduce tasks to TaskTrackers.
               Maintains all tasktrackers status like up/running , failed, recovered etc.
2.Task Tracker- Executes the tasks assigned by Job Tracker and sends status back.     
